PN,41801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FPharmacies are experiencing a surge in
OL,7,Fbookings for meningitis vaccines as
OL,8,Fpeople try to get jabs privately.
OL,10,FSuperdrug has said bookings for its
OL,11,Fservice are 65 times higher than a
OL,12,Fweek ago.
OL,14,FIt comes after the UK Health Security
OL,15,FAgency (UKHSA) confirmed that some
OL,16,Fcases in the Kent outbreak are
OL,17,Fmeningitis B.
OL,19,FHealth experts warned of "unequal
OL,20,Faccess" to protection based on the
OL,21,Fability to pay.
OL,26,@{D@ZOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
