OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FIn the coming days, officials will
OL,7,Flaunch a small vaccination programme
OL,8,Ffor students who live at Canterbury
OL,9,FCampus Halls of Residence at the
OL,10,FUniversity of Kent.
OL,12,FA jab for menB was introduced for
OL,13,Fbabies as past of the routine
OL,14,Fchildhood immunisation programme in
OL,15,F2015.
OL,17,FBut the majority of young people born
OL,18,Fbefore 2015 are not protected, unless
OL,19,Fthey have had the jab privately.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FA number of pharmacies offer the menB
OL,7,Fvaccine, including Superdrug, where it
OL,8,Fis available for children from the age
OL,9,Fof two months and adults aged up to 50.
OL,11,FA course of two to three doses is
OL,12,Frecommended, priced at #110 per dose.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Superdrug said: "At
OL,15,FSuperdrug, bookings at our nurse
OL,16,Fclinics for our meningitis service
OL,17,Fthis week have surged to 65 times the
OL,18,Flevel seen last week."
OL,26,@vD@dOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
