OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FAt Boots, the vaccination service is
OL,7,Ffor adults and children aged two and
OL,8,Fover costing #220 for two doses.
OL,10,FAt Well Pharmacy, the vaccine is
OL,11,Favailable for children from the age of
OL,12,Ftwo months and adults aged up to 50.
OL,14,FThe course includes two to three
OL,15,Fdoses, depending on age, at #110 each.
OL,17,FAsda also launched a meningitis
OL,18,Fvaccine service last year, with a full
OL,19,FmenB course available for #179.76.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
