FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FAppointment availability varies across
OL,7,Fthe country as of 11.30 on March 17.
OL,9,FThere were appointments available at
OL,10,FBoots in major cities including
OL,11,FLondon, but there are none currently
OL,12,Favailable at the Boots store in
OL,13,FCanterbury.
OL,15,FSuperdrug health clinics across the
OL,16,FSouth East also had appointments
OL,17,Favailable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, UKHSA said there have been
OL,7,F15 cases of meningitis reported to
OL,8,Fthem in Kent, up from 13 reported
OL,9,Fpreviously.
OL,11,FFour of these cases are confirmed to
OL,12,Fhave menB.
OL,14,FUKHSA officials investigating the
OL,15,Foutbreak, which has left two young
OL,16,Fpeople dead and others in hospital,
OL,17,Fsaid it would confirm the strain in
OL,18,Fother cases when the full results are
OL,19,Favailable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FExperts also said it "takes time for
OL,7,Fthe immune response to kick in" after
OL,8,Fvaccination and stressed that getting
OL,9,Fantibiotics to those exposed should be
OL,10,Fa priority.
OL,12,FOn Monday, hundreds of people who
OL,13,Fvisited Club Chemistry in Canterbury
OL,14,Fon March 5, 6 or 7 were told to come
OL,15,Fforward for preventative antibiotic
OL,16,Ftreatment as a "precautionary measure".
OL,26,@nD@VOUoD@_O]xD@POUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FProfessor Andrew Pollard, director of
OL,7,Fthe Oxford Vaccine Group at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Oxford, said: "The first
OL,9,Fquestion on vaccination is whether
OL,10,Fthis B strain is covered by the
OL,11,Fvaccine as this isn't always the case
OL,12,F` this takes time for the UKHSA to
OL,13,Fwork out in the laboratory and they
OL,14,Fare working round the clock on this.
OL,26,@pD@]OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,F"If it does match then B vaccines are
OL,7,Fgreat but it takes time for the immune
OL,8,Fresponse to kick in after the jab and
OL,9,Fso the absolute priority today is to
OL,10,Fensure that those who have been
OL,11,Fexposed get antibiotics to stop them
OL,12,Fdeveloping the disease or spreading
OL,13,Fthe B germs to others."
OL,15,FDr Eliza Gil, clinical lecturer at the
OL,16,FLondon School of Hygiene & Tropical
OL,17,FMedicine (LSHTM), added: "Some
OL,18,Ffamilies choose to access vaccination
OL,19,Fprivately as it is commercially
OL,20,Favailable on the high street from
OL,21,Fchemists.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@WO]yD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,F"This creates a situation where
OL,7,Fcurrently we have unequal access based
OL,8,Fon ability to pay."
OL,10,FThe charity Meningitis Now has called
OL,11,Ffor teenagers and young people to be
OL,12,Fvaccinated against meningitis B on the
OL,13,FNHS as part of its No Plan B for menB
OL,14,Fcampaign.
OL,16,FIt also says menB jabs should be
OL,17,Favailable on the high street "at a
OL,18,Ffair price".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SO]yD@^OUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FOn the NHS, the menB jab is
OL,7,Frecommended for babies aged eight
OL,8,Fweeks, followed by a second dose at 12
OL,9,Fweeks and a booster at one year.
OL,11,FOther routine childhood jabs,
OL,12,Fincluding the 6-in-1 and pneumococcal
OL,13,Fvaccines, can protect against
OL,14,Fmeningitis.
OL,16,FElsewhere, the menACWY vaccine is a
OL,17,Fsingle dose jab that protects against
OL,18,Ffour strains of meningococcal
OL,19,Fbacteria. It was also introduced in
OL,20,F2015.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FIt is offered to teenagers in school
OL,7,Fand is also available to those
OL,8,Fentering university, up to the age of
OL,9,F25.
OL,11,FThe National Pharmacy Association
OL,12,F(NPA) urged the NHS commission
OL,13,Fpharmacies to provide a catch-up
OL,14,Fservice for teenagers who missed their
OL,15,FmenACWY vaccine, and called for
OL,16,Freforms to the childhood vaccination
OL,17,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773835369
OL,3,CSurge in pharmacy bookings for
OL,4,Cmeningitis jabs amid Kent outbreak
OL,6,FNPA chairman Olivier Picard said:
OL,7,F"Some pharmacies are already seeing an
OL,8,Fuptick in patients contacting them to
OL,9,Fbook menACWY and menB vaccinations and
OL,10,Fwe anticipate this demand will
OL,11,Fcontinue to grow.
OL,13,F"Meningitis is a very serious illness
OL,14,Fbut the risk can be significantly
OL,15,Freduced through vaccination.
OL,17,F"Many parents may be unaware of the
OL,18,Frisks posed to older teenagers from
OL,19,Fmeningitis and the importance of
OL,20,Fgetting vaccinated."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
